# pyenv
#   For a library or app, you might want to share your .python-version.
#   Otherwise, uncomment the line below.
#.python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if the system requirements of the dependencies differ, the lock file can be excluded.
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock contains the resolved dependencies and should be tracked.
#poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, pdm.lock contains the resolved dependencies and should be tracked.
#pdm.lock

